# Frontend PRODUCTION build env (EXAMPLE — safe to commit; no secrets).
# VITE_API_BASE must point to the DEPLOYED backend HTTPS URL and is baked in at BUILD time.
# On Render, set this as the static site's build env var (do NOT rely on this example file for the
# real value). If it is missing at build, the SPA falls back to http://localhost:8000 and will fail
# in the cloud — this is the #1 deploy mistake.
VITE_API_BASE=https://benefitiq-api.onrender.com
